        <item>
            <title>PS5 Pro 官方拆機解構內部設計，液態金屬、新風扇設計令散熱效果更好、更寧靜</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/ps5-pro-teardown-2/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-teardown-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/ps5-pro-teardown-2/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 22 Apr 2025 11:43:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304504</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 近日公開 PlayStation 5 Pro 的拆解細節，揭示這款高階主機在散熱設計上的重大改良，成功解決原版 PS5 存在的液態金屬滲漏與過熱問題。透過更大面積風扇、重設扇葉形狀以及改良液態金屬塗層，PS5 Pro 帶來更穩定表現，為長時間遊玩提供穩妥支援。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769663_fd23f813.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304510" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769663_fd23f813-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769663_fd23f813-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769663_fd23f813.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/eff5991706e1e62ff196.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/eff5991706e1e62ff196-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/eff5991706e1e62ff196-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/eff5991706e1e62ff196.jpg 1088w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Sony PlayStation.Blog 官方網誌昨日（21 日）發表 PS5 Pro 主機拆解文章，展示了這部新主機針對原版 PS5 熱管理不足的問題作出多方面強化，特別是防止液態金屬冷卻系統出現滲漏。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513021_7d721965.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513021_7d721965-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513021_7d721965-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513021_7d721965.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674082_f307c712.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674082_f307c712-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674082_f307c712-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674082_f307c712.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769583_46267cd0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769583_46267cd0-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769583_46267cd0-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769583_46267cd0.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>針對主機整體散熱，PS5 Pro 配備比原版更大的風扇，並採用重新設計的扇葉，每片扇葉之間再加入更細小扇葉，進一步提升氣流效率，同時保持低噪音輸出。土田信也表示，遊戲主機的散熱設計必須平衡效能與靜音，這與一般風扇設計哲學不同，Sony 特別在氣流「安靜」輸出上下功夫，避免風扇噪音幹擾玩家沉浸感。</p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704509_9ceaf531.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304511" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704509_9ceaf531-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704509_9ceaf531-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704509_9ceaf531.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲對比之下 PS5 Pro 風扇（左）比起原版 PS5（右）體積更大</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704469_601c3dd8.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704469_601c3dd8-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704469_601c3dd8-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456704469_601c3dd8.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲每片扇葉之間再加入更細小扇葉，進一步提升氣流效率，同時保持低噪音輸出。</p><p>主機外觀方面，PS5 Pro 保留家族設計語言，並加入三條橫向通風縫隙，這些被工程團隊稱為「葉片」的設計，不但美觀，同時提升氣流流通能力。後方排氣口面積亦增大，配合底部與背部進氣，提升整體散熱效能。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513031_2d1629d6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513031_2d1629d6-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513031_2d1629d6-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456513031_2d1629d6.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>主機內部，PS5 Pro 主機板尺寸較前代稍大，因應新增電路設計需求，調整風扇位置與 I/O 端口排列，將 HDMI、LAN、USB 等接口位置上移，以配合更緊湊主機板結構。為減少電磁幹擾，主機板金屬屏蔽層以多顆螺絲固定，確保電磁波幹擾控制在安全標準以下，防止影響其他電子設備運作。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272827.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272827-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272827-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272827.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272833.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272833-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272833-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042272833.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲翻開保護金屬片就可看到主機板</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512961_2815e14e.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512961_2815e14e-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512961_2815e14e-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512961_2815e14e.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>PS5 Pro 主機板採用更多層數，將訊號通道藏於內層，有效提升記憶體訊號傳輸速度。記憶體配置方面，PS5 Pro 採用 8 顆升級版 GDDR6 記憶體，負責遊戲高效能渲染，並新增一顆 DDR5 記憶體，專門處理作業系統等低速任務，實現性能分流。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769613_85832efe.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769613_85832efe-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769613_85832efe-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769613_85832efe.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲圖中紅圈位置為新增的記憶體</p><p>PS5 Pro 內部結構經過重新設計，最引人注目的改動包括液態金屬冷卻區域新增細槽，令冷卻效果更穩定。Sony 工程團隊領導成員土田信也（Shinya Tsuchida）指出，這些細槽有助固定液態金屬位置，防止在主機垂直擺放時流出。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674017_fe2353e1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304519" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674017_fe2353e1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674017_fe2353e1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674017_fe2353e1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456876270_f0a57d3e.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456876270_f0a57d3e-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456876270_f0a57d3e-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456876270_f0a57d3e.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>散熱器部分，PS5 Pro 配備更多銅製熱導管與鋁製散熱鰭片，鰭片分成兩段式設計，貼合主機內部結構，進一步提升散熱效率，應對高效能遊戲負載。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512956_02cd0b9a.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512956_02cd0b9a-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512956_02cd0b9a-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456512956_02cd0b9a.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>電源供應部分，PS5 Pro 採用比現有 PS5 輸出高出 48 瓦的電源模組，尺寸亦相應增大，以應對主機更高的功耗需求。電源模組曲面設計與機身內部完美貼合，細節甚至刻有「Sony Interactive Entertainment」字樣，確保安裝方向無誤。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769563_60f2b887.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304523" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769563_60f2b887-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769563_60f2b887-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54456769563_60f2b887.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>網絡連接方面，PS5 Pro 搭載最新 Wi-Fi 7 模組，成為首批支援此規格的遊戲主機，雖則當初標準尚未正式發布，Sony 工程團隊依然提前完成測試認證，保證玩家未來數年享受高速穩定的無線連接。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674022_1d8b90aa.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674022_1d8b90aa-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674022_1d8b90aa-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/54455674022_1d8b90aa.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>總結而言，PS5 Pro 雖在外觀與核心硬件提升幅度有限，但透過散熱與內部結構優化，成功解決原版 PS5 的散熱隱患，為玩家帶來更穩定遊戲體驗。對於重視性能穩定與長時間遊戲的玩家，PS5 Pro 可算是一個值得考慮的升級選擇。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/ps5-pro-teardown-2/game-channel/">PS5 Pro 官方拆機解構內部設計，液態金屬、新風扇設計令散熱效果更好、更寧靜</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
